item.p:
\tan(x): 
                Domain = any real number except odd multiples of \pi/2; 
                Range =(-\infty,\infty).

\arctan(x): 
                Domain =(-\infty,\infty);
                Range = (-\pi/2,\pi/2).

\exp(x) = e^x: 
                Domain = (-\infty,\infty); 
                Range =(0,\infty).

\ln(x): 
                Domain =(0,\infty);
                Range = (-\infty,\infty).
